text: Wiesław Bocheński (born 7 January 1944) is a Polish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle +97 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Poland Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw
